'''15号州际公路'''（{{lang-en|Interstate 15}}，简称 {{lang|en|I}}-15）是连接美国加利福尼亚州[[圣地亚哥_(加利福尼亚州)|圣地亚哥]]至[[美加边界|美加边界]]的南北向[[州际公路系统|州际公路]]，途经[[亚利桑那州|亚利桑那州]]西北部的[[莫哈维县|莫哈维县]]。該公路在亚利桑那州境内全长47.36公里，皆行經該州人口較不密集的[[亚利桑那地带|亚利桑那地带]]，并亦行经风景优美的[[维尔京河大峡谷|维尔京河大峡谷]]闻名。公路从[[内华达州|内华达州]][[克拉克县_(内华达州)|克拉克县]][[梅斯基特_(内华达州)|梅斯基特]]东北边境进入亚利桑那州並整体保持东北走向，从[[犹他州|犹他州]][[圣乔治_(犹他州)|圣乔治]]西南边境離開亚利桑那州。

公路在經過[[小田_(亚利桑那州)|小田]]前与91号莫哈維縣縣道大致平行，通過小田後进入维尔京河大峡谷。從内华达州抵達小田的路段早在20世纪60年代初便通车，但峡谷内的路段直至1973年才完工。該段在完成后刷新美国鄉間高速公路修建成本的新纪录。

== 路线详解 ==
[[File:I15storm3.jpg|thumb]]

15号州际公路在亚利桑那州境內的路段是屬於[[加美墨走廊|加美墨]]贸易走廊的一部分<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff | url = http://www.canamex.org/CanaMexUSA.asp | title = CANAMEX Highway in the USA | publisher = CANAMEX Corridor Coalition | accessdate = 2012-10-12 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2012-10-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121012232233/http://www.canamex.org/canamexusa.asp }}</ref>。此路段與15號州際公路犹他州路段都被指定为“退伍军人纪念公路”<ref name="arizonalaw">{{cite web | url = http://www.azleg.state.az.us/legtext/42leg/1r/bills/hjr2003s.htm | title = HJR2003 - 421R — S Ver | accessdate = 2008-04-13 | author = [[亚利桑那州议会|Arizona State Legislature]] | publisher = State of Arizona | archivedate = 2008-04-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080413091424/http://www.azleg.state.az.us/legtext/42leg/1r/bills/hjr2003s.htm }}</ref><ref name="utahlaw">{{cite web | url = http://le.utah.gov/~code/TITLE72/htm/72_04_020100.htm | title = Utah Code Section 72-4-201 | accessdate = 2013-12-26 | publisher = State of Utah | author = Utah State Legislature | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131226193843/http://le.utah.gov/~code/TITLE72/htm/72_04_020100.htm | archivedate = 2013-12-26 }}</ref>，其中亚利桑那州段平均每天通行汽车量约2.8万辆<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff | publisher = Arizona Department of Transportation | archivedate = 2019-12-31 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191231213805/https://azdot.gov/sites/default/files/2019/05/2018-AADT-INTERSTATES.pdf | url = https://azdot.gov/sites/default/files/2019/05/2018-AADT-INTERSTATES.pdf | title = 2018 AADTs (includes K, D and T factors) - Interstates | accessdate = 2020-07-07 }}</ref>。

公路从内华达州[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]和梅斯基特（{{lang|en|Mesquite}}）东北部进入亚利桑那州後与91号莫哈維縣縣道大致平行，朝東北方的维尔京河前進。在位於[[小田_(亚利桑那州)|小田]]的八号出口，15号州际公路與转向北上以避开维尔京河大峡谷的91号莫哈維縣縣道相交。通過八号出口後，15号州际公路首次跨越维尔京河，接著與一地方道路形成九号出口，采用右进右出的[[辅路|辅路]]设计。<ref name="USGS" />。
[[File:I-15_Arizona_Virgin_River_Gorge.jpg|thumb]]

离开九号出口后，公路进入维尔京河大峡谷，其沿途地形逐漸变得崎岖<ref name="USGS">{{cite map | cartography = [[美国地质调查局|United States Geological Survey]] | title = Topographic Maps | publisher = [[美国地质调查局|U.S. Geological Survey]] | url = https://ngmdb.usgs.gov/topoview/viewer/#15/36.9209/-113.8592 | accessdate = 2020-07-07 | archive-date = 2019-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191010031100/https://ngmdb.usgs.gov/topoview/viewer/#15/36.9209/-113.8592 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。公路兩側為可高出公路150米的[[石灰岩|石灰岩]]悬崖；路肩有多处可供停车以方便觀賞大峽谷的景觀。<ref name="Scenic driving">{{cite book | title = Scenic Driving Arizona | url = https://archive.org/details/scenicdrivingari0000gree | last = Green | first = Stewart | year = 2003 | location = Old Saybrook, CT | publisher = Globe Pequot | series = Falcon Guide | isbn = 0-7627-2701-2 | edition = 2nd | page = [https://archive.org/details/scenicdrivingari0000gree/page/24 24]}}</ref>峡谷内呈北高南低，並有五座桥梁跨越维尔京河<ref name="bridges">{{cite web | author = Arizona Department of Transportation | date = 2015-02-28 | publisher = Arizona Department of Transportation | url = https://apps.azdot.gov/files/bridge/inventory/bridge-inventory-all-districts.pdf | format = PDF | title = Arizona State Highway System Bridge Record | access-date = 2020-07-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200707140407/https://apps.azdot.gov/files/bridge/inventory/bridge-inventory-all-districts.pdf | archivedate = 2020-07-07 }}</ref>。公路整体沿著維爾京河蜿蜒前进，但也有几处弯道是透過[[钻炸法|钻炸法]]建成<ref name="USGS" />。

由於峡谷在18号出口處略有变宽，[[美國內政部土地管理局|聯邦土地管理局]]於1970年代曾在該出口旁設立一[[公路服务区|公路服务区]]，但於1996年關閉<ref>{{citeweb|url=https://www.deseret.com/1996/5/25/19244482/arizona-shutting-down-popular-i-15-rest-area|title=ARIZONA SHUTTING DOWN POPULAR I-15 REST AREA|author= Deseret News|publisher=Deseret News|date=1996-05-25|access-date=2022-06-04}}</ref>。2002年，[[亞利桑那州交通部|亞利桑那州交通部]]放棄該[[公路服务区|公路服务区]]的土地使用權，並轉由聯邦土地管理局全權管理。<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff | publisher = Arizona Department of Transportation | title = Arizona Right-of-Way Resolution 2002-12-A-062 | date = 2002-12-20 | accessdate = 2019-03-27 | url = http://www.azhighwaydata.com/resolutions/pdf/resolutionfull/2002-12-A-062.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2019-03-27 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190327090856/http://azhighwaydata.com/resolutions/pdf/resolutionfull/2002-12-A-062.pdf }}</ref>。

公路在18号出口後继续与维尔京河平行，但偏移距离逐漸加寬<ref name="USGS" />。公路两側可見到包括[[红荆|红荆]]、[[梣树|梣树]]、[[棉白杨|棉白杨]]、[[柳树|柳树]]和[[短叶丝兰|短叶丝兰]]等树在內，春天時還可看到如[[沙漠球葵|沙漠球葵]]、[[万寿菊属|万寿菊]]和[[沙地马鞭草|沙地马鞭草]]等花草点缀<ref name="Scenic driving" />。公路在22.5英里處最后一次跨过维尔京河，沿黑岩峡谷继续向东，然后略朝东北转向进入地势更平坦的区域并经过27号出口<ref name="USGS" />。

公路接近28英里处建有由亚利桑那州交通部机动车司和[[犹他州交通部|犹他州交通部]]汽车运输司人员共同管理的[[称量站|称量站]]和[[口岸|口岸]]，将亚利桑那州段和不远处的犹他州段正式分隔<ref name="USGS" />。之後15号州际公路進入犹他州，通往[[圣乔治_(犹他州)|圣乔治]]和[[盐湖城|盐湖城]]。<ref name="USGS" />

== 历史 ==
[[File:Rockcut15.jpg|thumb]]

此路段的前身最早可追溯到其中一條[[老西班牙步道|老西班牙步道]]（{{lang|en|Old Spanish Trail}}）：阿米霍路線（{{lang|en|Armijo Route}}）。該步道在离开[[南加利福尼亚州|南加利福尼亚州]]後在小田與[[老西班牙步道#主步道|主步道]]分離，經過维尔京河大峡谷後跨过州界抵达[[四角落|四角落]]区域<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff | publisher = [[美国国家公园管理局|National Park Service]] | url = http://imgis.nps.gov/Geocortex/Viewer/NPS/Viewer.html?Viewer=National%20Historic%20Trails | title = Old Spanish National Historic Trail | accessdate = 2011-10-16 | archivedate = 2011-10-16 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111016224211/http://imgis.nps.gov/Geocortex/Viewer/NPS/Viewer.html?Viewer=National%20Historic%20Trails }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.nps.gov/olsp/planyourvisit/places-to-go.htm | title = The Old Spanish Trail Interactive Map | accessdate = 2020-07-07 | publisher = National Park Service | archive-date = 2020-07-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200713120318/https://www.nps.gov/olsp/planyourvisit/places-to-go.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

20世纪20年代，[[箭头公路|箭头公路]]和91号美国国道先后通车，人们可以驾车从内华达州和犹他州沿路北上，在犹他州转向东进抵达圣乔治<ref name="1926 Rand McNally">{{cite map | publisher = [[兰德麦奈利|Rand McNally]] | title = Auto Road Atlas | year = 1926 | url = http://broermapsonline.org/online/NorthAmerica/UnitedStates/Southwest/Arizona/unitedstates1926ra_060.html | accessdate = 2020-07-07 | archive-date = 2020-07-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200711054052/http://broermapsonline.org/online/NorthAmerica/UnitedStates/Southwest/Arizona/unitedstates1926ra_060.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

计划修建州际公路期间，联邦政府决定將原本91号美国国道的路線（从内华达州到犹他州的圣乔治）縮短19公里，让新建的公路通过维尔京河大峡谷。此舉能在充分展現峽谷风景的同时有更低的地势以便卡車通行<ref name="inch" /><ref name="costly" />。内华达州至维尔京河大峡谷路段率先在20世纪60年代初修好，大弯曲湿地上的桥梁于1962年建成，维尔京河上靠近小田的桥梁在1964年完成。1965年，跨過黑岩路（27號出口）的高架橋通车。<ref name="bridges" />
[[File:Cedarpkt.jpg|thumb]]

峡谷内的公路建设非常困難，直到1973年12月14日才全面开放<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081026051250/http://www.interstate50th.org/history/2006-12-14.shtml | deadurl = yes | year = 2006 | url = http://interstate50th.org/history/2006-12-14.shtml | accessdate = 2008-10-26 | title = Today in Interstate History | publisher = American Association of State Highway and Transportation Officials | archivedate = 2008-10-26 }}</ref>。为加快建设速度，犹他州曾将部分联邦公路基金借给亚利桑那州<ref name="costly">{{cite news | date = 1969-11-14 | title = Costliest Interstate To Be in Arizona | page = D10 | work = The News-Press | location = Fort Myers, Florida | agency = Associated Press | via = Newspapers.com | accessdate = 2020-07-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180717071027/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21934838/costliest_interstate_to_be_in_arizona/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21934838/costliest-interstate-to-be-in-arizona/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2018-07-17 }}{{free access}}</ref>：儘管这条公路對亚利桑那州的交通幫助不大，在连接[[盐湖城|盐湖城]]與[[拉斯维加斯|拉斯维加斯]]和西南方向的[[洛杉矶|洛杉矶]]上起到重要作用<ref>{{cite news | date = 1972-06-16 | title = Bids Called on First Paving Work On Scenic Virgin River Gorge Road | page = 2 | work = Arizona Daily Sun | location = Flagstaff, Arizona | archivedate = 2018-07-17 | deadurl = no | via = Newspapers.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180717095916/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21934902/bids_called_on_first_paving_work_on/ | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21934902/bids-called-on-first-paving-work-on/ | accessdate = 2020-07-07 }}{{free access}}</ref>。

獲得更多預算後，工程仍面临重重困难。峡谷内的山洪和流沙经常导致设备和建筑材料一夜之间不翼而飞。更甚，1969年10月飞入峡谷侦察地形的直升机因大风坠毁，造成一名飞行员丧生。为穿越峡谷内崎岖复杂的地形，施工隊必須從[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]借來一台[[沼泽越野车|沼泽越野车]]來協助建設這段公路<ref name="problems">{{cite news | newspaper = Arizona Daily Sun | location = Flagstaff, Arizona | title = I-15 Project Surrounded by Problems | page = 13 | date = 1973-12-18}}</ref>，接著需在维尔京河上再修四座大桥，其中最西面的桥和从西往东第三座桥（承载北行车道）于1972年完工。所有桥梁皆在1973年前完成<ref name="bridges" />。

路段正式通车前就被稱為亚利桑那州最秀丽的公路。《[[亚利桑那公路|亚利桑那公路]]》（''{{lang|en|Arizona Highways}}''）杂志1988年曾发文，称这截公路非但没有减少來自大自然鬼斧神工的魅力，反而令景色更加迷人。维尔京河共改道12次之多，导致这段公路成为全美造价最高的乡村高速公路，平均每公里耗费620万美元（按2007年[[物價水準|物價水準]]計算）。<ref name="inch">{{cite news | date = 1972-11-22 | title = Costliest freeway nears completion | page = 31 | work = Tucson Daily Citizen | url = https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21934880/costliest-freeway-nears-completion/ | via = Newspapers.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20180717095951/https://www.newspapers.com/clip/21934880/costliest_freeway_nears_completion/ | accessdate = 2020-07-07 | archivedate = 2018-07-17 | deadurl = no }}{{free access}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Staff | publisher = Federal Highway Administration | archivedate = 2020-06-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200629180012/https://www.environment.fhwa.dot.gov/env_topics/historic_pres/highways_list.aspx | url = https://www.environment.fhwa.dot.gov/env_topics/historic_pres/highways_list.aspx | title = Final List of Nationally and Exceptionally Significant Features of the Federal Interstate Highway System | accessdate = 2020-07-07 }}</ref>
